modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod adds one new Del Stryker archetype to the archetypes.xml. This is just an example of how to create additional archetypes to use within the game.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/DelStryker/Delmod/tree/master/Delmod_Archetypes)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/11141-del-stryker-a17-modlet-collection/).
